initiative: EV last-mile expansion (40 vans) | owner: Fleet Strategy | status: on track | impact: -310t CO₂ annualized | due: 2026-09-30
initiative: Collections automation | owner: Finance Ops | status: on track | impact: -6 days DSO target | due: 2026-07-31

